We're going to look at definitions of&nbsp;
quadrilaterals and polygons. I hope&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:42.000 --> 00:09:46.140
you'll join me for that. I'm Norman&nbsp;
Wildberger. Thanks for listening.

